WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.230
Hey, good morning family. I'm going

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:03.869
to talk to you all about the time

00:00:03.869 --> 00:00:03.879
when

00:00:03.879 --> 00:00:05.590
Jesus woke me up in the middle

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:08.750
of the night and

00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:13.230
ministered to me. This

00:00:13.240 --> 00:00:16.029
was around October of

00:00:16.039 --> 00:00:19.710
2014, and this experience forever

00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:22.590
changed my life. I just feel

00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:24.269
in my heart that when I first started

00:00:24.279 --> 00:00:25.990
out on YouTube, I tried to tell you

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:28.950
all what He said, and I thought I

00:00:28.950 --> 00:00:28.960
would

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:32.030
do it again because it gets

00:00:32.040 --> 00:00:34.709
buried by the algorithm. It gets

00:00:34.719 --> 00:00:36.549
buried at the bottom and nobody sees it

00:00:36.549 --> 00:00:36.559
among

00:00:36.559 --> 00:00:38.709
all these new faces here,

00:00:38.719 --> 00:00:41.670
and I want to tell people

00:00:41.680 --> 00:00:43.310
because this was an experience

00:00:43.320 --> 00:00:45.029
I had with Him that changed my life

00:00:45.039 --> 00:00:47.389
forever. So,

00:00:47.399 --> 00:00:51.950
here we go. I was sleeping, and

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:54.110
all of a sudden, I felt a tap

00:00:54.120 --> 00:00:55.470
on my right shoulder right

00:00:55.480 --> 00:00:58.430
here. I was just laying in bed

00:00:58.440 --> 00:01:01.189
on my side and I felt this

00:01:01.199 --> 00:01:03.709
wake up, and I heard this wake

00:01:03.709 --> 00:01:03.719
up—I'm

00:01:03.719 --> 00:01:07.190
talking audibly, 'Wake up.'He touched me, and I woke up

00:01:07.190 --> 00:01:07.200
and

00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:09.030
looked over, and

00:01:09.040 --> 00:01:12.310
Jesus was standing in my room.

00:01:12.320 --> 00:01:15.230
Most people say, 'Was this a

00:01:15.230 --> 00:01:15.240
vision?'No,

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:18.030
this was not a vision. This was real. I'm

00:01:18.040 --> 00:01:20.630
talking about Him manifesting in my house.

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:22.749
This was one of only

00:01:22.759 --> 00:01:24.710
two times that it

00:01:24.710 --> 00:01:24.720
wasn't an

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:26.990
open-eyed vision;

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:29.149
this was a face-to-face experience

00:01:29.159 --> 00:01:31.990
with Him touching my shoulder

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:35.389
and waking me up out of my sleep.

00:01:35.399 --> 00:01:37.510
It startled me so much when this

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:39.230
happened because I

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:41.069
didn't recognize Him at the time.

00:01:41.069 --> 00:01:41.079
When

00:01:41.079 --> 00:01:42.990
you're waking up out of a sleep and

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:44.670
rubbing your eyes, I

00:01:44.670 --> 00:01:44.680
looked

00:01:44.680 --> 00:01:46.789
over and Jesus was standing there. I

00:01:46.789 --> 00:01:46.799
felt

00:01:46.799 --> 00:01:48.510
His glory and presence, and

00:01:48.520 --> 00:01:50.910
my

00:01:50.920 --> 00:01:53.149
initial reaction was, 'Am I dying? I'm

00:01:53.159 --> 00:01:56.029
going home; He's coming to get me.'But He

00:01:56.039 --> 00:01:58.630
said, 'I've come to answer your

00:01:58.630 --> 00:01:58.640
prayers.'I

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:00.870
asked,

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:02.749
'Lord, what's happening? What's

00:02:02.759 --> 00:02:05.389
going on?'All of a sudden, I looked at

00:02:05.399 --> 00:02:08.430
my floor, and my floor

00:02:08.440 --> 00:02:11.869
was alive. The glory of the Lord was

00:02:11.879 --> 00:02:15.750
so strong that the floor was

00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:18.030
breathing. There was a

00:02:18.040 --> 00:02:22.030
portal opened in my floor. I

00:02:22.030 --> 00:02:22.040
was

00:02:22.040 --> 00:02:24.270
sitting on the edge of my bed, and

00:02:24.270 --> 00:02:24.280
I flipped

00:02:24.280 --> 00:02:26.710
my feet over the edge,

00:02:28.360 --> 00:02:30.990
looking at that

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:34.550
portal below my feet. Jesus was standing

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:37.190
right there on my right hand,

00:02:37.190 --> 00:02:37.200
and

00:02:37.200 --> 00:02:39.350
I

00:02:39.350 --> 00:02:39.360
was

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:41.830
looking at this portal.

00:02:41.840 --> 00:02:44.270
The portal was alive, and I could feel

00:02:44.280 --> 00:02:46.990
the air breathing; it was blowing my

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:49.949
hair. At that

00:02:49.959 --> 00:02:52.550
time, I had a little bit more hair

00:02:52.550 --> 00:02:52.560
than

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:54.390
I have

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:58.390
now. I could

00:02:58.400 --> 00:03:01.949
feel the breeze from the portal

00:03:01.959 --> 00:03:03.710
breathing. It was moving

00:03:03.720 --> 00:03:06.550
like a waterfall, but the light was

00:03:06.560 --> 00:03:08.750
moving down and up

00:03:08.760 --> 00:03:12.070
like a whirlpool.

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:14.030
He said to me—and mind

00:03:14.040 --> 00:03:15.789
you, my wife was sleeping next to me, she

00:03:15.799 --> 00:03:17.270
never knew any of this happened, she was

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:19.030
out

00:03:19.040 --> 00:03:22.070
cold—I

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:23.390
said, 'Lord, what do you

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:25.309
want me to do?'He said,

00:03:25.319 --> 00:03:28.350
'I want you to jump inside that portal.'I said, 'You want me to jump?'He said, 'Brandon, trust me.'I looked at him, shocked, because this was all happening so fast. If anybody experienced

00:03:28.350 --> 00:03:28.360
this, it would mess with them. Jesus was standing there in a beautiful white robe, and His hair was flowing because of the air from the

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:31.070
portal. I said, 'Okay, Lord,'and all of a sudden, I pushed myself off the bed and went straight down into that tunnel. It felt like Mario Brothers when you go into the tunnel;

00:03:31.070 --> 00:03:31.080
it transported you to another part. When I jumped inside that hole, I was taken to the past. I was standing at a hospital where my wife and I had our daughter, Megan.

00:03:31.080 --> 00:03:34.030
He said, 'Brandon,

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:37.390
I'm

00:04:37.400 --> 00:04:39.390
giving you a chance. You've asked Me and

00:04:39.400 --> 00:04:40.870
asked Me, and I hear the

00:04:40.880 --> 00:04:44.110
cries of your heart to go back in time.'You always

00:04:44.110 --> 00:04:44.120
asked Me,

00:04:44.120 --> 00:04:47.189
'If I could just go back in time,

00:04:49.240 --> 00:04:51.150
Lord,

00:04:51.160 --> 00:04:54.270
when she got her shot, I

00:04:54.280 --> 00:04:56.670
could stop that and keep

00:04:56.680 --> 00:04:59.749
her from getting this severe

00:04:59.749 --> 00:04:59.759
autism.'I

00:04:59.759 --> 00:05:01.350
always said it. I

00:05:01.350 --> 00:05:01.360
I'd

00:05:01.360 --> 00:05:03.150
clean the bathrooms of the church,

00:05:03.150 --> 00:05:03.160
vacuuming

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:04.590
the halls,

00:05:04.590 --> 00:05:04.600
doing

00:05:04.600 --> 00:05:06.150
everything over and over, thinking, 'If

00:05:06.150 --> 00:05:06.160
I could

00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:08.990
just have gone back in time and warned myself, I wouldn't have let this wreck my life.'I literally said it all the time: 'I wish I could have

00:05:16.350 --> 00:05:16.360
a

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:26.189
redo.'When

00:05:33.840 --> 00:05:36.270
He stood there, He said, 'I'm

00:05:36.280 --> 00:05:38.270
going to give you the time to go and

00:05:38.280 --> 00:05:41.830
change the future. I want you to go and

00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:45.070
tell yourself.'I ran up the stairs to the

00:05:45.070 --> 00:05:45.080
doctor's office

00:05:45.080 --> 00:05:47.189
on the fourth floor.

00:05:52.759 --> 00:05:55.749
I busted through the

00:05:55.759 --> 00:06:00.029
doors and saw my younger

00:06:00.029 --> 00:06:00.039
self

00:06:00.039 --> 00:06:03.070
sitting there with my daughter and

00:06:03.080 --> 00:06:04.950
wife. They were getting ready to

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:08.629
administer the shot. I said,

00:06:08.639 --> 00:06:11.909
'Stop!'Just

00:06:11.919 --> 00:06:15.950
like that, the

00:06:15.950 --> 00:06:15.960
young me

00:06:15.960 --> 00:06:19.670
froze.

00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:22.150
I told the nurse to stop

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:25.309
because I saw my older

00:06:25.309 --> 00:06:25.319
self

00:06:25.319 --> 00:06:27.150
there.

00:06:27.160 --> 00:06:29.830
All of a

00:06:29.840 --> 00:06:32.430
sudden, Jesus came and said, 'I want to

00:06:32.440 --> 00:06:35.550
show you the power of a choice. I

00:06:35.560 --> 00:06:37.749
want to show you what

00:06:37.759 --> 00:06:41.430
happens by a choice.'He threw His

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:43.710
hand open,

00:06:43.710 --> 00:06:43.720
and

00:06:43.720 --> 00:06:46.670
a screen appeared in front of my face.

00:06:46.680 --> 00:06:50.629
Everything froze in time. In

00:06:50.629 --> 00:06:50.639
the vision,

00:06:50.639 --> 00:06:54.029
Megan didn't get that shot, but He

00:06:54.039 --> 00:06:57.430
painted

00:06:57.430 --> 00:06:57.440
the

00:06:57.440 --> 00:07:01.390
outcome

00:07:01.390 --> 00:07:01.400
of

00:07:01.400 --> 00:07:04.469
each

00:07:04.479 --> 00:07:06.950
year in front of me. He said, 'Brandon, I want to show

00:07:06.960 --> 00:07:09.189
you what happened by this

00:07:09.189 --> 00:07:09.199
choice.'I

00:07:09.199 --> 00:07:10.550
had

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:12.550
told Him, 'Lord,

00:07:12.560 --> 00:07:14.110
You've called me to be a healing

00:07:14.120 --> 00:07:16.230
evangelist, to lay hands

00:07:16.240 --> 00:07:18.749
on the sick, but I feel

00:07:18.749 --> 00:07:18.759
like a hypocrite

00:07:18.759 --> 00:07:20.749
because

00:07:20.759 --> 00:07:22.550
my own daughter

00:07:22.550 --> 00:07:22.560
is

00:07:22.560 --> 00:07:24.589
still overcoming. I've laid hands on her

00:07:24.599 --> 00:07:27.189
a thousand times and

00:07:27.199 --> 00:07:30.510
never felt

00:07:30.520 --> 00:07:32.070
the anointing

00:07:32.070 --> 00:07:32.080
go

00:07:32.080 --> 00:07:34.629
into

00:07:34.639 --> 00:07:36.110
her.'I

00:07:36.120 --> 00:07:37.629
had

00:07:37.639 --> 00:07:39.150
always kept this private; I

00:07:39.160 --> 00:07:41.029
wouldn't even let

00:07:41.039 --> 00:07:42.830
anybody say

00:07:42.830 --> 00:07:42.840
the

00:07:42.840 --> 00:07:45.830
word

00:07:45.830 --> 00:07:45.840
'autistic.'If

00:07:45.840 --> 00:07:48.350
you did, I wanted to

00:07:48.360 --> 00:07:49.589
fight you. That's how strong

00:07:49.599 --> 00:07:51.909
it was to me because faith calls

00:07:51.919 --> 00:07:53.110
those things that be not as though they

00:07:53.120 --> 00:07:55.189
were. I

00:07:55.199 --> 00:07:56.589
got flaky about it and wouldn't

00:07:56.599 --> 00:07:58.270
let doctors

00:07:58.280 --> 00:08:00.430
diagnose her

00:08:00.440 --> 00:08:02.350
because

00:08:02.360 --> 00:08:03.830
life and

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:05.430
death are in the power of the tongue.

00:08:09.039 --> 00:08:10.909
I

00:08:10.919 --> 00:08:13.149
knew there was a serious issue

00:08:13.159 --> 00:08:17.149
because of what happened, and I was

00:08:17.159 --> 00:08:21.189
scared.

00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:28.070
It was bondage. She

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:29.790
would rock in the corner and scream

00:08:29.800 --> 00:08:31.790
all night long.

00:08:31.800 --> 00:08:33.430
It was literal

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:36.110
hell on Earth for years before I

00:08:36.110 --> 00:08:36.120
allowed

00:08:36.120 --> 00:08:38.149
them to diagnose her and get her

00:08:38.159 --> 00:08:40.230
therapies. I was

00:08:40.230 --> 00:08:40.240
trying to

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:42.230
believe God by

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:43.469
faith because

00:08:43.469 --> 00:08:43.479
of

00:08:43.479 --> 00:08:45.470
the

00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:47.750
prophecies over my life.

00:08:47.750 --> 00:08:47.760
The

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:49.509
Lord

00:08:49.509 --> 00:08:49.519
showed

00:08:49.519 --> 00:08:52.829
me,

00:08:52.839 --> 00:08:55.110
'Brandon, I want

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:59.430
to show you what happens with Megan now;

00:08:59.430 --> 00:08:59.440
she

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:01.269
is developing

00:09:01.269 --> 00:09:01.279
normally,

00:09:01.279 --> 00:09:05.069
but you're not

00:09:05.079 --> 00:09:10.069
changing. The pressure from her

00:09:10.079 --> 00:09:13.710
circumstance changes you. It puts you

00:09:13.720 --> 00:09:15.550
through the Refiner's

00:09:15.550 --> 00:09:15.560
Fire.'He

00:09:15.560 --> 00:09:19.269
told me, 'Brandon, I

00:09:19.279 --> 00:09:23.389
did not do this. I did not cause her to

00:09:23.399 --> 00:09:27.269
be autistic, but whatever the devil turns

00:09:27.279 --> 00:09:29.470
for bad, I will turn it for good

00:09:29.480 --> 00:09:32.829
in your favor. No matter how bad

00:09:32.839 --> 00:09:35.030
the circumstance is, I will always turn

00:09:35.040 --> 00:09:37.829
it for good.

00:09:41.360 --> 00:09:44.790
I'm not the one who caused the

00:09:44.800 --> 00:09:47.470
autism; it's a fallen world where things

00:09:47.470 --> 00:09:47.480
happen.'That's

00:09:47.480 --> 00:09:48.750
the

00:09:48.750 --> 00:09:48.760
picture

00:09:48.760 --> 00:09:50.590
He

00:09:50.600 --> 00:09:52.389
painted for me. I want to

00:09:52.399 --> 00:09:54.190
say exactly what He said, but it's been

00:09:54.200 --> 00:09:55.750
so long that I'm forgetting some

00:09:55.760 --> 00:09:57.670
words, so bear with me.

00:09:59.680 --> 00:10:03.550
He painted

00:10:03.560 --> 00:10:04.949
the picture

00:10:04.959 --> 00:10:06.670
year

00:10:06.670 --> 00:10:06.680
by

00:10:06.680 --> 00:10:09.190
year. He said, 'Brandon, do you see right

00:10:09.200 --> 00:10:11.910
here? You have a lot of anger

00:10:11.920 --> 00:10:13.750
issues that you're still

00:10:13.760 --> 00:10:15.910
overcoming. You were very

00:10:15.920 --> 00:10:18.470
verbally abusive to your wife.'I

00:10:18.470 --> 00:10:18.480
was;

00:10:18.480 --> 00:10:20.590
I belittled her a lot when I

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:22.710
first got married. I was young and

00:10:22.720 --> 00:10:25.230
stupid.

00:10:25.240 --> 00:10:28.150
He said, 'Because of this,

00:10:28.150 --> 00:10:28.160
a

00:10:28.160 --> 00:10:31.750
wall

00:10:31.760 --> 00:10:34.030
develops between you and your

00:10:34.040 --> 00:10:37.990
wife over time. Megan

00:10:37.990 --> 00:10:38.000
is

00:10:38.000 --> 00:10:42.430
developing normally, but your wife

00:10:42.440 --> 00:10:44.910
leaves you right here.'He pointed out

00:10:44.920 --> 00:10:47.069
the year.

00:10:50.079 --> 00:10:53.069
'She takes your daughter and

00:10:53.069 --> 00:10:53.079
moves

00:10:53.079 --> 00:10:54.629
to

00:10:54.639 --> 00:10:57.790
Texas. You see her every

00:10:57.800 --> 00:11:00.470
two weeks

00:11:00.470 --> 00:11:00.480
because

00:11:00.480 --> 00:11:02.430
you don't have full custody.

00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:14.790
Diana gets

00:11:14.800 --> 00:11:17.670
remarried to another man.'He showed me the man.

00:11:20.760 --> 00:11:22.949
He said,

00:11:22.959 --> 00:11:26.470
'Then you become very bitter and angry

00:11:26.480 --> 00:11:28.470
because of the choices you've

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:31.150
made. You're off track with your

00:11:31.160 --> 00:11:33.790
call

00:11:33.800 --> 00:11:37.629
because

00:11:37.639 --> 00:11:41.150
this pressure

00:11:41.160 --> 00:11:43.430
from having a child with special needs is

00:11:43.440 --> 00:11:46.230
molding your character. It's breaking you

00:11:46.240 --> 00:11:50.910
down and making you pliable in My hands.

00:11:50.920 --> 00:11:56.230
I did not do

00:11:56.240 --> 00:11:59.949
it, but I will use

00:11:59.949 --> 00:11:59.959
it.'The

00:11:59.959 --> 00:12:04.190
pressure of my daughter's situation changed me. In the alternate timeline where she was normal, I

00:12:04.200 --> 00:12:07.910
saw

00:12:07.920 --> 00:12:09.710
that

00:12:13.030 --> 00:12:13.040
my

00:12:15.519 --> 00:12:18.430
son was

00:12:18.440 --> 00:12:19.310
never

00:12:19.320 --> 00:12:22.910
born,

00:12:22.910 --> 00:12:22.920
and

00:12:22.920 --> 00:12:25.710
the

00:12:25.720 --> 00:12:29.150
daughter we will

00:12:29.150 --> 00:12:29.160
have

00:12:29.160 --> 00:12:33.949
in the future would not be born.

00:12:33.959 --> 00:12:36.829
There is a call on her life for things I'm going to

00:12:36.829 --> 00:12:36.839
do in the next

00:12:36.839 --> 00:12:38.790
thousand years

00:12:38.800 --> 00:12:41.269
that

00:12:41.279 --> 00:12:43.310
would

00:12:43.320 --> 00:12:46.670
not be set in motion.

00:12:46.680 --> 00:12:49.269
He said, 'You say you've messed up

00:12:49.279 --> 00:12:51.870
your life and can't be used

00:12:51.880 --> 00:12:55.189
now, but

00:12:55.199 --> 00:12:59.509
Brandon, all things work together for

00:12:59.519 --> 00:13:02.150
good for those that love the Lord

00:13:02.160 --> 00:13:04.670
and are called according to His

00:13:04.680 --> 00:13:07.710
purpose. You're not big enough to mess up

00:13:07.720 --> 00:13:08.629
your

00:13:08.639 --> 00:13:12.550
life

00:13:12.550 --> 00:13:12.560
or

00:13:12.560 --> 00:13:14.030
derail

00:13:14.030 --> 00:13:14.040
it.

00:13:14.040 --> 00:13:16.750
If you stay in right standing

00:13:19.199 --> 00:13:22.670
and seek Me daily,

00:13:26.000 --> 00:13:27.949
I will take what the devil meant

00:13:27.959 --> 00:13:31.350
for bad and turn it for good.

00:13:31.360 --> 00:13:34.509
There's

00:13:34.519 --> 00:13:37.389
not enough power in hell to derail your

00:13:37.399 --> 00:13:40.629
call,

00:13:40.639 --> 00:13:43.430
son.'So,

00:13:45.350 --> 00:13:45.360
I

00:13:49.269 --> 00:13:49.279
saw

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:56.590
each year play out.

00:14:08.920 --> 00:14:10.829
Having a child with special

00:14:10.839 --> 00:14:14.269
needs molded me into who I am

00:14:14.279 --> 00:14:16.870
today.

00:14:24.920 --> 00:14:26.749
If you've never been a caretaker for

00:14:26.749 --> 00:14:26.759
someone

00:14:26.759 --> 00:14:29.150
with special needs,

00:14:29.160 --> 00:14:32.230
you

00:14:32.240 --> 00:14:34.670
don't

00:14:34.680 --> 00:14:37.509
know

00:14:37.519 --> 00:14:39.470
the tears. She only slept

00:14:39.480 --> 00:14:42.430
two hours a night

00:14:42.440 --> 00:14:44.150
for

00:14:44.160 --> 00:14:46.629
years. I would go to work

00:14:46.639 --> 00:14:48.550
so tired I'd fall asleep

00:14:48.560 --> 00:14:50.150
against the wall

00:14:50.160 --> 00:14:52.269
while

00:14:52.279 --> 00:14:54.670
cleaning toilets. We were barely

00:14:54.680 --> 00:14:58.030
making

00:14:58.030 --> 00:14:58.040
it

00:14:58.040 --> 00:15:02.030
on food stamps.

00:15:02.040 --> 00:15:04.949
My wife would

00:15:04.949 --> 00:15:04.959
be

00:15:04.959 --> 00:15:07.470
at home crying, and I'd

00:15:07.470 --> 00:15:07.480
have

00:15:07.480 --> 00:15:08.910
to

00:15:08.910 --> 00:15:08.920
drive

00:15:08.920 --> 00:15:12.629
Megan

00:15:17.199 --> 00:15:19.110
around

00:15:19.120 --> 00:15:21.269
just so she would fall asleep.

00:15:25.639 --> 00:15:27.749
She wouldn't wear

00:15:27.759 --> 00:15:30.790
clothes for years because the

00:15:30.790 --> 00:15:30.800
texture

00:15:30.800 --> 00:15:34.269
weirded

00:15:34.279 --> 00:15:35.670
her out.

00:15:55.800 --> 00:15:57.990
We were ecstatic just to get

00:15:58.000 --> 00:16:00.749
her to

00:16:00.759 --> 00:16:03.110
wear a diaper or a nightgown. All

00:16:06.959 --> 00:16:08.670
that

00:16:13.959 --> 00:16:17.389
time was pressure,

00:16:17.399 --> 00:16:19.470
and it molds you.

00:16:19.480 --> 00:16:21.030
What happens to a diamond

00:16:21.030 --> 00:16:21.040
when

00:16:21.040 --> 00:16:23.470
coal is under pressure?

00:16:23.480 --> 00:16:27.150
It's transformed into something

00:16:27.160 --> 00:16:30.069
beautiful.

00:16:31.920 --> 00:16:34.590
Just like it is

00:16:34.600 --> 00:16:37.829
with the caterpillar

00:16:37.839 --> 00:16:40.829
in a cocoon. If

00:16:40.839 --> 00:16:43.590
you remove that cocoon

00:16:43.600 --> 00:16:45.870
before it's time, the

00:16:45.870 --> 00:16:45.880
butterfly won't

00:16:45.880 --> 00:16:48.150
have the strength

00:16:56.000 --> 00:16:59.509
to fly. The pressure

00:16:59.519 --> 00:17:02.910
of the cocoon makes

00:17:02.910 --> 00:17:02.920
the

00:17:02.920 --> 00:17:05.870
butterfly

00:17:07.600 --> 00:17:11.230
who it is.

00:17:16.640 --> 00:17:18.350
We think

00:17:32.919 --> 00:17:34.549
the storms of life are

00:17:34.559 --> 00:17:36.350
destroying us, but

00:17:36.360 --> 00:17:39.070
they are making us who we are.

00:17:39.070 --> 00:17:39.080
We ask God to remove

00:17:39.080 --> 00:17:41.350
the pressure,

00:17:49.000 --> 00:17:52.470
but He says, 'All

00:17:52.480 --> 00:17:54.669
things are possible to him that believe.

00:17:54.679 --> 00:17:56.590
I'm going to turn

00:17:56.600 --> 00:17:59.310
it around for

00:17:59.320 --> 00:18:00.750
good.'Don't

00:18:03.190 --> 00:18:03.200
just

00:18:05.080 --> 00:18:08.230
embrace the struggle; fight and

00:18:08.240 --> 00:18:10.630
resist it.

00:18:22.280 --> 00:18:25.230
Submit to God,

00:18:25.240 --> 00:18:28.870
resist the devil, and he will flee. The

00:18:28.870 --> 00:18:28.880
process

00:18:28.880 --> 00:18:31.830
of

00:18:31.830 --> 00:18:31.840
the

00:18:31.840 --> 00:18:34.190
fight

00:18:35.830 --> 00:18:35.840
is

00:18:38.520 --> 00:18:41.270
what changes us.

00:18:43.640 --> 00:18:47.310
In this situation,

00:18:47.320 --> 00:18:51.230
God did not do

00:18:51.230 --> 00:18:51.240
this—the

00:18:51.240 --> 00:18:53.590
devil comes to kill, steal, and

00:18:53.590 --> 00:18:53.600
destroy—but

00:18:55.110 --> 00:18:55.120
God

00:18:55.120 --> 00:18:56.710
used

00:18:56.720 --> 00:18:59.430
it

00:18:59.440 --> 00:19:02.270
to develop

00:19:02.280 --> 00:19:05.390
who I

00:19:07.950 --> 00:19:07.960
am.

00:19:10.919 --> 00:19:12.549
He told me

00:19:12.559 --> 00:19:14.470
He was going to use me for ministry and

00:19:14.470 --> 00:19:14.480
that

00:19:14.480 --> 00:19:16.350
the

00:19:16.350 --> 00:19:16.360
intensity of

00:19:16.360 --> 00:19:18.470
the

00:19:18.470 --> 00:19:18.480
storm

00:19:18.480 --> 00:19:21.110
would subside.

00:19:25.240 --> 00:19:26.909
We

00:19:26.919 --> 00:19:29.470
go from glory to glory

00:19:29.470 --> 00:19:29.480
and

00:19:29.480 --> 00:19:31.669
mature to handle

00:19:31.669 --> 00:19:31.679
the

00:19:31.679 --> 00:19:33.630
pressure better.

00:19:35.360 --> 00:19:39.070
The

00:19:40.720 --> 00:19:42.750
Potter is molding

00:19:42.750 --> 00:19:42.760
the

00:19:42.760 --> 00:19:45.310
clay. We have

00:19:45.320 --> 00:19:47.350
this treasure in earthen vessels

00:19:47.350 --> 00:19:47.360
so

00:19:47.360 --> 00:19:48.830
the power

00:19:48.830 --> 00:19:48.840
is

00:19:48.840 --> 00:19:51.230
of Him and not of us. If you

00:19:51.240 --> 00:19:54.190
think you've derailed your life because you were a

00:19:54.200 --> 00:19:56.830
bad person

00:19:59.840 --> 00:20:02.710
or a victim of

00:20:02.720 --> 00:20:04.870
abuse,

00:20:04.880 --> 00:20:07.590
you

00:20:07.600 --> 00:20:10.310
are

00:20:10.320 --> 00:20:12.750
not

00:20:12.760 --> 00:20:14.750
disqualified. God

00:20:23.720 --> 00:20:26.029
will

00:20:26.039 --> 00:20:30.909
take beauty from

00:20:30.919 --> 00:20:33.470
ashes.

00:20:36.440 --> 00:20:39.029
That pain is

00:20:39.039 --> 00:20:40.190
going to help you help

00:20:40.190 --> 00:20:40.200
someone

00:20:40.200 --> 00:20:41.669
else

00:20:41.679 --> 00:20:44.190
walking through it.

00:20:44.200 --> 00:20:45.950
You'll

00:20:45.960 --> 00:20:47.710
have compassion that others won't. When I

00:20:47.710 --> 00:20:47.720
see

00:20:47.720 --> 00:20:49.430
a

00:20:49.430 --> 00:20:49.440
child

00:20:49.440 --> 00:20:51.310
with

00:20:58.320 --> 00:20:59.909
special needs

00:20:59.919 --> 00:21:01.510
in

00:21:01.520 --> 00:21:04.590
the store,

00:21:04.600 --> 00:21:07.870
my spirit weeps

00:21:19.120 --> 00:21:21.669
because I've been through that pain.

00:21:31.440 --> 00:21:33.470
You can

00:21:33.470 --> 00:21:33.480
tell

00:21:33.480 --> 00:21:36.830
them, 'You can make it

00:21:36.840 --> 00:21:38.190
too.'There

00:21:39.750 --> 00:21:39.760
were

00:21:41.840 --> 00:21:43.430
days

00:21:43.440 --> 00:21:45.070
I wanted to drive my car off

00:21:45.080 --> 00:21:48.430
a bridge because

00:21:48.430 --> 00:21:48.440
the

00:21:48.440 --> 00:21:50.909
pain was

00:21:50.909 --> 00:21:50.919
so

00:21:50.919 --> 00:21:52.750
much,

00:21:57.200 --> 00:21:59.590
but I fought through it because I knew

00:21:59.600 --> 00:22:01.950
God had a plan.

00:22:01.950 --> 00:22:01.960
It

00:22:01.960 --> 00:22:04.630
was

00:22:04.630 --> 00:22:04.640
raw

00:22:04.640 --> 00:22:06.789
and

00:22:06.789 --> 00:22:06.799
real.

00:22:06.799 --> 00:22:09.510
There

00:22:09.510 --> 00:22:09.520
were

00:22:09.520 --> 00:22:12.149
days

00:22:16.510 --> 00:22:16.520
I

00:22:21.400 --> 00:22:22.870
didn't have enough

00:22:22.880 --> 00:22:25.470
money for a gallon of milk, and

00:22:30.990 --> 00:22:31.000
I

00:22:36.080 --> 00:22:37.710
felt

00:22:37.720 --> 00:22:39.350
all

00:22:39.360 --> 00:22:41.549
alone.

00:22:41.549 --> 00:22:41.559
But

00:22:41.559 --> 00:22:44.110
my

00:22:44.110 --> 00:22:44.120
hope

00:22:44.120 --> 00:22:46.510
is

00:22:46.510 --> 00:22:46.520
built

00:22:46.520 --> 00:22:48.590
on

00:23:05.960 --> 00:23:08.590
nothing less

00:23:08.600 --> 00:23:11.430
than Jesus'blood and righteousness.

00:23:11.440 --> 00:23:14.470
I believe with all my heart that by the

00:23:14.480 --> 00:23:18.350
stripes of Jesus, Megan is healed.

00:23:18.360 --> 00:23:21.110
The full

00:23:21.120 --> 00:23:23.990
manifestation is sometimes a process,

00:23:24.000 --> 00:23:26.510
but

00:23:29.200 --> 00:23:32.350
seeing change

00:23:32.350 --> 00:23:32.360
is

00:23:32.360 --> 00:23:33.710
still a

00:23:33.720 --> 00:23:35.310
miracle.

00:23:45.320 --> 00:23:46.390
I

00:23:56.360 --> 00:23:59.510
trust Him with all my

00:23:59.520 --> 00:24:01.630
heart

00:24:01.630 --> 00:24:01.640
and

00:24:01.640 --> 00:24:03.830
lean not

00:24:03.830 --> 00:24:03.840
onto

00:24:03.840 --> 00:24:05.990
my own understanding. I

00:24:08.830 --> 00:24:08.840
could

00:24:13.720 --> 00:24:16.029
get upset and

00:24:16.029 --> 00:24:16.039
ask,

00:24:16.039 --> 00:24:18.430
'Lord,

00:24:18.440 --> 00:24:20.669
why hasn't the

00:24:20.679 --> 00:24:22.710
full manifestation

00:24:22.710 --> 00:24:22.720
happened

00:24:22.720 --> 00:24:25.590
yet? Why is she still not

00:24:27.870 --> 00:24:27.880
talking?'But

00:24:29.039 --> 00:24:30.950
I say, 'I trust

00:24:30.960 --> 00:24:34.710
You, Father. Not my will, but Yours be

00:24:36.799 --> 00:24:38.669
done.'I

00:24:40.760 --> 00:24:42.230
used

00:24:45.799 --> 00:24:49.230
to

00:24:52.440 --> 00:24:55.549
complain that

00:24:55.549 --> 00:24:55.559
I couldn't

00:24:55.559 --> 00:24:57.070
go out and

00:24:57.070 --> 00:24:57.080
minister,

00:24:57.080 --> 00:24:58.190
but

00:24:58.200 --> 00:25:00.789
the Lord said,

00:25:00.799 --> 00:25:03.990
'Brandon, Megan does not validate My word.

00:25:04.000 --> 00:25:06.669
My

00:25:06.679 --> 00:25:09.510
word validates itself. It is a pillar

00:25:09.510 --> 00:25:09.520
that

00:25:09.520 --> 00:25:12.389
stands alone. I don't need

00:25:12.389 --> 00:25:12.399
her

00:25:12.399 --> 00:25:14.350
full manifestation for you to

00:25:16.039 --> 00:25:18.269
tell people I'm a Healer.

00:25:18.279 --> 00:25:21.110
My

00:25:21.120 --> 00:25:25.750
word is

00:25:33.640 --> 00:25:35.789
enough.'In

00:25:42.760 --> 00:25:45.029
Galatians 3:13, Christ

00:25:45.039 --> 00:25:46.950
redeemed us from the curse of the law. That

00:25:46.950 --> 00:25:46.960
is

00:25:46.960 --> 00:25:49.190
the

00:25:49.200 --> 00:25:51.870
foundation. I'm not moved by

00:25:51.880 --> 00:25:54.909
what I see or feel;

00:25:54.919 --> 00:25:58.310
I'm moved by what the Word of God says.

00:25:58.320 --> 00:26:00.950
So, back to

00:26:02.750 --> 00:26:02.760
the

00:26:04.760 --> 00:26:07.110
portal—He

00:26:08.549 --> 00:26:08.559
told

00:26:10.320 --> 00:26:13.149
me,

00:26:15.640 --> 00:26:18.149
'Go

00:26:18.159 --> 00:26:21.909
back and give your daughter a hug.

00:26:21.919 --> 00:26:25.029
Thank her right now for

00:26:25.029 --> 00:26:25.039
how

00:26:25.039 --> 00:26:26.830
her

00:26:26.840 --> 00:26:29.470
life

00:26:29.470 --> 00:26:29.480
is

00:26:29.480 --> 00:26:33.110
changing

00:26:33.110 --> 00:26:33.120
yours.

00:26:33.120 --> 00:26:36.750
Stay in an atmosphere of

00:26:36.750 --> 00:26:36.760
praise.'I

00:26:36.760 --> 00:26:39.389
had

00:26:39.389 --> 00:26:39.399
been

00:26:39.399 --> 00:26:41.110
complaining all the

00:26:41.120 --> 00:26:43.389
time. I

00:26:51.190 --> 00:26:51.200
went

00:26:58.360 --> 00:26:59.750
home and held Megan

00:26:59.750 --> 00:26:59.760
and

00:26:59.760 --> 00:27:02.389
said, 'I love you, and

00:27:02.389 --> 00:27:02.399
Daddy's

00:27:02.399 --> 00:27:04.990
sorry

00:27:05.000 --> 00:27:07.310
I didn't hear Him right.

00:27:07.320 --> 00:27:09.230
Your life is changing

00:27:14.590 --> 00:27:14.600
me.'Don't

00:27:23.320 --> 00:27:24.830
give

00:27:29.110 --> 00:27:29.120
up.

00:27:34.360 --> 00:27:37.110
All things work together for

00:27:37.120 --> 00:27:39.389
good.

00:27:50.519 --> 00:27:52.950
Keep on keeping on.

00:27:54.880 --> 00:27:57.190
Jesus is the

00:27:57.200 --> 00:27:59.190
Healer yesterday, today, and

00:27:59.200 --> 00:28:01.430
forever.

00:28:05.640 --> 00:28:07.310
Do not give up on your

00:28:07.320 --> 00:28:09.549
unsaved loved ones or

00:28:09.549 --> 00:28:09.559
those who

00:28:09.559 --> 00:28:12.190
haven't seen

00:28:12.190 --> 00:28:12.200
their

00:28:12.200 --> 00:28:13.789
full manifestation

00:28:24.630 --> 00:28:24.640
yet.

00:28:34.480 --> 00:28:37.710
Stay on God's side.

00:28:40.440 --> 00:28:44.230
See

00:28:44.230 --> 00:28:44.240
Him

00:28:44.240 --> 00:28:47.990
as a good God no matter how

00:28:48.000 --> 00:28:50.789
hard the trial.

00:28:53.950 --> 00:28:53.960
The

00:29:02.149 --> 00:29:02.159
pressure

00:29:05.720 --> 00:29:08.830
changed

00:29:11.440 --> 00:29:15.149
me.

00:29:18.120 --> 00:29:20.509
If

00:29:29.230 --> 00:29:29.240
people

00:29:37.720 --> 00:29:40.950
knew

00:29:40.960 --> 00:29:42.950
who I was back then, they'd

00:29:42.950 --> 00:29:42.960
see that

00:29:42.960 --> 00:29:45.590
person died a long time ago.

00:29:53.440 --> 00:29:57.070
The Lord has molded

00:29:57.080 --> 00:29:59.029
me into who I am today.

00:30:00.789 --> 00:30:00.799
You

00:30:03.360 --> 00:30:05.149
are

00:30:06.840 --> 00:30:08.669
not big

00:30:08.679 --> 00:30:11.149
enough to mess your life up.

00:30:24.519 --> 00:30:26.830
The steps of the righteous are

00:30:26.840 --> 00:30:29.190
ordered by the Lord.

00:30:31.240 --> 00:30:33.710
Whatever the devil meant

00:30:33.720 --> 00:30:37.029
for bad, the Lord will turn for

00:30:37.039 --> 00:30:38.549
good.

00:30:41.799 --> 00:30:43.590
Trust

00:30:43.600 --> 00:30:46.509
Him

00:30:46.519 --> 00:30:47.830
with all your heart.

00:31:19.120 --> 00:31:21.549
Father, I thank You

00:31:21.559 --> 00:31:24.310
for every person

00:31:24.320 --> 00:31:25.549
here.

00:31:25.559 --> 00:31:27.549
I thank You

00:31:31.279 --> 00:31:33.990
that no weapon

00:31:34.000 --> 00:31:36.870
formed against us

00:31:36.870 --> 00:31:36.880
shall

00:31:36.880 --> 00:31:39.629
prosper.

00:31:41.880 --> 00:31:43.990
You have a plan for

00:31:44.000 --> 00:31:47.629
us

00:31:50.559 --> 00:31:54.350
to

00:31:58.120 --> 00:31:59.669
prosper and be

00:31:59.679 --> 00:32:02.070
in health.

00:32:04.600 --> 00:32:08.230
You are

00:32:08.240 --> 00:32:09.870
the great Creator

00:32:09.870 --> 00:32:09.880
with

00:32:09.880 --> 00:32:11.509
a

00:32:11.519 --> 00:32:13.350
plan

00:32:13.360 --> 00:32:15.389
for every one of us.

00:32:17.360 --> 00:32:20.750
If the devil throws

00:32:20.750 --> 00:32:20.760
a

00:32:20.760 --> 00:32:23.629
log in our path,

00:32:23.639 --> 00:32:25.629
You'll turn it into

00:32:25.639 --> 00:32:27.190
toothpicks.

00:32:47.480 --> 00:32:50.230
We praise

00:32:50.240 --> 00:32:52.310
You in the

00:32:52.320 --> 00:32:55.110
storms

00:32:55.110 --> 00:32:55.120
and

00:32:55.120 --> 00:32:57.110
in the good times. We

00:33:13.919 --> 00:33:16.590
say God

00:33:16.600 --> 00:33:19.950
is faithful.

00:33:23.960 --> 00:33:27.149
I speak

00:33:27.159 --> 00:33:29.909
healing over their bodies

00:34:00.399 --> 00:34:03.549
now. Now faith is the substance of

00:34:03.559 --> 00:34:04.950
things hoped for. I believe for

00:34:04.950 --> 00:34:04.960
'now.'Megan's healing is

00:34:04.960 --> 00:34:09.629
now. I thank You for their deliverance now.

00:34:49.320 --> 00:34:51.869
We thank You,

00:34:56.919 --> 00:34:58.710
Lord, that You

00:34:58.710 --> 00:34:58.720
are

00:34:58.720 --> 00:35:00.670
the

00:35:00.670 --> 00:35:00.680
Deliverer.

00:35:00.680 --> 00:35:03.270
I plead

00:35:03.280 --> 00:35:05.710
the blood of Jesus

00:35:05.720 --> 00:35:08.150
over their marriages,

00:35:08.160 --> 00:35:10.069
homes, and children.

00:35:38.800 --> 00:35:41.710
Today is the day

00:35:46.280 --> 00:35:48.270
the

00:35:48.280 --> 00:35:51.430
Lord has made; we will rejoice and be

00:35:51.440 --> 00:35:53.870
glad in it.

00:35:53.880 --> 00:35:56.710
Rejoice

00:35:56.710 --> 00:35:56.720
in

00:35:56.720 --> 00:35:59.990
the

00:35:59.990 --> 00:36:00.000
Lord

00:36:00.000 --> 00:36:02.670
always,

